description = "Athena Web 2 — browser-based tactical second-screen companion for Arma 3. Requires the original Athena mod (by Bus) and relay. No gameplay addon is provided here: do not load @AthenaWeb2 as a server/client mod. Run AthenaWeb.exe to launch the bridge server, then open http://localhost:3000 in any browser on your local network.";
