overview = "Athena Web 2 is a browser-based second-screen tactical map for Arma 3. It connects to the original Athena relay and renders a full military cartography map with live unit tracking — straight from your browser, on any device on your local network. Requires: Athena mod by Bus (Workshop ID 1181881736). @AthenaWeb2 itself is not meant to be loaded as an Arma gameplay mod.";
author = "SgtFoose";
